text: “Læa ca raluk khna thi rea di chwy phwk cea hı phn cak phwkphxng khxng fi rxa wnddy thi phwk khea bangkhab khukhey phwk cea sung kar thrman xan rayræng phwk khea kha brrda lukphuchay khxng phwk cea læa wi chiwit brrda lukphuhying khxng phwk cea læa nı reuxng nan khux kar thdsxb xan sakhay cak ra ceakhxng phwk cea”
